---+++ Create New Topic

To create a new topic, select the %BASEWEB%.TopicType you'd like to create from dropdown menu below: <br />
<form action="%SCRIPTURLPATH%/view%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%BASEWEB%/CreateNewTopic">
*Create New:*  <select name="type" onchange="this.form.submit()">
  <option value="%URLPARAM{"type" default=""}%">%URLPARAM{"type" default="Select..."}%</option><option value="blank" >blank topic</option>
%DBQUERY{ "Classification= 'TopicType'" web="%BASEWEB%" format= "<option>$topic</option>" separator=" "}%</select> 
</form>
